I need to form an equilateral triangle with other robots, centered at (150, 100). First, I need to find out my current position and if there are other robots.
```
[
  { "cmd": "sense" }
]
```

I have reached my target location (150, 71.13). Now I need to wait for other robots to reach their target locations. I will set a timeout for 60 seconds.

```
